{"tid":185875,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鼓起勇氣去做一件事，可惜家人唔支持:-(","createTime":"2017-04-03T18:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T03:27:19.000Z","uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4090b46b99fa88e198c486ac0d958d20fa757176","tid":185875,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:38:56.000Z","msg":"最近機緣巧合下識到個中學同校舊生，同佢合作。雖然個offer 幾好paid 但係唔太穩定。而且做落佢地幾個合夥人都覺我ok ，而且我亦都嘗試係唔同範疇幫佢地expand 。<br />\n<br />\n今晚鼓起勇氣同屋企人講，可惜老豆覺得我不切實際，又覺得我一定失敗，覺得返工應該踏踏實實朝九晚五。又反話我咁樣做可以搵幾多錢。又講廢柴返飲食都萬幾蚊個月之類。<br />\n<br />\n我承認我一直以嚟份人都比較頹，屋企人都覺得我做嘢hea底。一直以嚟都唔清楚自己目標，但今次我好想去試。我問自己，冇屋企人撐我到底可以行幾遠？<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 今年23歲，份工同it 有少許關係，係新科技嚟。依家類似接job 等client approach 咁既模式，所以返工時間唔定。 行頭太窄，再講會自爆，對唔住各位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b728736444485654bb0fcfb92ffb8b16f3e045","tid":185875,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:43:34.000Z","msg":"可能1999 sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啱啱嘈完，平伏唔到，強忍眼淚水"},{"pid":"b55a31c116753459a0afe46f06c76b5e4b472ea9","tid":185875,"uid":7757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:45:24.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e7318f63fa88421622f60597fd9167a698b023","tid":185875,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:50:51.000Z","msg":"我爸覺得我係懶散，唔相信呢行會成功。但係我係後面有付出心血去嘗試，雖然談不上係咩大努力，但係我但確有為呢件事留意外左身邊相關既機會，一啲潛在既客人。"},{"pid":"20bf67ad7d26010e115412650328de675357c3f1","tid":185875,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T18:54:01.000Z","msg":"但係有時會問自己係咪應該妥協"},{"pid":"64230ade3b4f492d97d88f91e058f863c436f984","tid":185875,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bcc4d06818db629b62cbf7306cfc91fe854c78","tid":185875,"uid":67064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:14:58.000Z","msg":"你嘅人生屬於你自己，既然你依家都諗到有嘢係想去試想去做嘅，咁就放手去做喇。唔係等幾時？呢個機會過後你幾時又會再遇到另外一個機會？錯過咗你確定自己唔會後悔？你依家妥協唔通又會有機會發圍咩？做咗失敗咗最多咪返返你原先嘅狀態，你唔會有咩損失噶。俾啲信心自己做決定喇。加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：淨係識鼓勵人 唔識鼓勵自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30ccee67d7bc6e74d99f6560e47ba6cf8a4e473","tid":185875,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:18:39.000Z","msg":"如果唔係屋企斷絕關係 去馬吧 睇你有冇勇氣"},{"pid":"5c5dc62aa8a46f75e1b302a7523b279247d9fbf9","tid":185875,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T19:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9em4uJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9em4uJ.jpg&h=425b69ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4QBL7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4QBL7G.jpg&h=4258d146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35e6cffd97a65483776081a66c1090df0795ad7b","tid":185875,"uid":10256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T21:34:24.000Z","msg":"試下游說屋企人<br />\n再唔得就用行動去做比佢地睇<br />\n仲要記住唔好令佢地覺得你鬥緊氣 而係為自己目標而努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"1806c87968a9fd816b153f0911972f3e3a8d05ea","tid":185875,"uid":9347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"